title: Hold'em Poker 3D-Deluxe Edition
description:
It's Texas Hold 'Em in real 3D! Play in Tournament mode just like the games you've seen on TV. Play against 75+ challenging players, each with their unique styles of play! Tired of playing against pre-set AI computer players that fold when you bet? Customized Skill Levels allow you to change and adjust the player attitude levels. Includes unlimited table combos and cheat modes! Deal me in!

LAN/ONLINE

Singleplayer


Requisitos do Sistema:
Windows 98, Windows XP, Windows Me
Memory: 128 MB
DirectX: 9.0c
CPU: P3 500
